item.title: CVE-2020-5756|2024-08-04T08:39:25.704Z -- tenable -- grandstream%20gwn7000
item.description: Grandstream GWN7000 firmware version 1.0.9.4 and below allows authenticated remote users to modify the system's crontab via undocumented API. An attacker can use this functionality to execute arbitrary OS commands on the router.
